spirent.methodology.RunSqlCommand.DbJsonString: {"sql_operations": [{"sql_statement": [{"static": "DROP TABLE IF EXISTS NoPacketTemp"}], "db_information": {"db_name": "SUMMARY"}}, {"report": {"explanation": "Frames were detected", "display_name": "Iteration Frame Results", "report_group": "GROUP_2", "report_verdict": {"passed_verdict_explanation": "Packets were detected by the Analyzer", "sql_for_verdict": [{"static": "SELECT CASE COUNT(*) WHEN 0 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END"}, {"static": "FROM sqlite_master WHERE type='table' AND name='NoPacketTemp'"}], "apply_test_verdict": true, "failed_verdict_explanation": "No frames were detected by the Analyzer"}}, "temp_table_name": "NoPacketTemp", "sql_statement": [{"static": "SELECT Sb.FixedFrameLength AS \"Frame Size (bytes)\", (SELECT DISTINCT FixedLoad FROM GeneratorConfig) AS \"Load (%)\", ROUND(AvgLatency, 2) AS \"Avg Latency (us)\", MinLatency AS \"Min Latency (us)\", MaxLatency AS \"Max Latency (us)\", SigFrameCount + DroppedFrameCount - DuplicateFrameCount AS 'Total Frames', TxRes.PortName AS \"Tx Port\", RxRes.PortName AS \"Rx Port\" FROM RxEotStreamResults AS RxRes JOIN TxEotStreamResults AS TxRes JOIN Streamblock AS Sb ON RxRes.ParentStreamBlock = TxRes.ParentStreamblock AND TxRes.ParentStreamblock = Sb.Handle AND SigFrameCount=0"}], "db_information": {"db_name": "LAST_ITERATION"}}, {"sql_statement": [{"static": "DROP TABLE IF EXISTS ThresholdTemp"}], "db_information": {"db_name": "SUMMARY"}}, {"report": {"explanation": "Average Latency check against threshold", "display_name": "Iteration Trial Results", "report_group": "GROUP_2", "report_verdict": {"passed_verdict_explanation": "Average Latency within threshold", "sql_for_verdict": [{"static": "SELECT CASE COUNT(*) WHEN 0 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END"}, {"static": "FROM sqlite_master WHERE type='table' AND name='ThresholdTemp'"}], "apply_test_verdict": true, "failed_verdict_explanation": "Average Latency exceeded threshold"}}, "temp_table_name": "ThresholdTemp", "sql_statement": [{"static": "SELECT Sb.FixedFrameLength AS \"Frame Size (bytes)\", (SELECT DISTINCT FixedLoad FROM GeneratorConfig) AS \"Load (%)\", ROUND(AvgLatency, 2) AS \"Avg Latency (us)\", MinLatency AS \"Min Latency (us)\", MaxLatency AS \"Max Latency (us)\", SigFrameCount + DroppedFrameCount - DuplicateFrameCount AS \"Total Frames\", TxRes.PortName AS \"Tx Port\", RxRes.PortName AS \"Rx Port\" FROM RxEotStreamResults AS RxRes JOIN TxEotStreamResults AS TxRes JOIN Streamblock AS Sb ON RxRes.ParentStreamBlock = TxRes.ParentStreamblock AND TxRes.ParentStreamblock = Sb.Handle AND AvgLatency >"}, {"dynamic": 100000}], "db_information": {"db_name": "LAST_ITERATION"}}, {"sql_statement": [{"static": "CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS MethRfc2544LatencyIterations ('FrameSize' INTEGER, 'Load' FLOAT, 'Trial' INTEGER, 'MinLatency' FLOAT, 'MaxLatency' FLOAT, 'TotalLatency' FLOAT, 'FrameCount' INTEGER, 'Latency' FLOAT, 'TxPort' VARCHAR, 'RxPort' VARCHAR)"}], "db_information": {"db_name": "SUMMARY"}}, {"temp_table_name": "MethRfc2544LatencyIterations", "sql_statement": [{"static": "SELECT Sb.FixedFrameLength AS 'FrameSize', (SELECT DISTINCT FixedLoad FROM GeneratorConfig) AS 'Load',"}, {"dynamic": "5"}, {"static": "AS 'Trial', MinLatency, MaxLatency, TotalLatency, SigFrameCount AS 'FrameCount', ROUND(AvgLatency, 2) AS 'Latency', TxRes.PortName AS 'TxPort', RxRes.PortName AS 'RxPort'"}, {"static": "FROM RxEotStreamResults AS RxRes JOIN TxEotStreamResults AS TxRes JOIN StreamBlock AS Sb On RxRes.ParentStreamBlock = TxRes.ParentStreamBlock AND TxRes.ParentStreamBlock = Sb.Handle"}], "db_information": {"db_name": "LAST_ITERATION"}}]}
